description: Tastefully renovated (2024) City Point Single-Family on a convenient private way with one car parking (Not Deeded). This home is a great condo alternative, with an open floor plan on the main level and two en-suite bedrooms on the 2nd level. Other features include HVAC (2 zones), a rear deck with patio yard, 1/2 bath on the living level, and lots of storage in the unfinished basement.
